  "comment": "he BeamZ MHL1912 LED moving head kit is a set of powerful wash moving heads designed to light up any stage or dance floor. Each head is powered by 19x 12W RGBW (4-in-1) LEDs with 3 individually controllable sections for creating eye-catching effects and colors. The linear motorized zoom allows you to focus a beam up to 8° or open up to 30° to cover a wider area with ease. Equipped with DMX, built-in auto programs and presets, including a master/slave mode. Perfect for stage shows, productions, events, DJ, Bands, Venues, and more. Supplied as a pair with a custom made heavy-duty road case to protect your fixtures while in transit or storage.",
